<div class="crumbs"><a href="/index.html">Home</a> / <a href="/leagues.html">Leagues</a> / <span>CPBL · Taiwan</span></div>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-flag">Taiwan · Chinese Professional Baseball League · 2026 Season</div>
    <div class="hero-country">
      <span class="hero-flag-emoji">🇹🇼</span>
      <div>
        <div class="hero-title">CPBL</div>
        <div class="hero-full">Chinese Professional Baseball League · 中華職業棒球大聯盟</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-lede">
      Taiwan's top flight went from regional curiosity to <strong>Premier12 world champions</strong>. Chinese Taipei won the 2024 tournament, defeating Japan 4-0 in the Tokyo Dome final. CPBL's profile has never been higher. Six teams, a fierce 120-game season, and one beautifully unusual detail: the <strong>Wei Chuan Dragons stream home games free on YouTube</strong> to build international audience. It works.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div><div class="hs-num">6</div><div class="hs-lbl">Teams</div></div>
      <div><div class="hs-num">120</div><div class="hs-lbl">Games / Team</div></div>
      <div><div class="hs-num">UTC+8</div><div class="hs-lbl">CST · ET +12</div></div>
      <div><div class="hs-num gold-hs">2024</div><div class="hs-lbl">Premier12 Champs</div></div>
      <div><div class="hs-num">1990</div><div class="hs-lbl">Founded</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page">

  <div class="watch-window">
    <div class="ww-title">⚡ When to Watch CPBL from the US</div>
    <div class="ww-lede">CPBL games are the <strong>most US-friendly of any Asian league</strong>. Weekday games start at 18:35 CST = <strong>6:35 AM ET</strong> — workable for insomniacs and West Coast night owls. Weekend day games at 14:00 CST = <strong>2:00 AM ET</strong>, the prime window for East Coast fans watching before bed.</div>
    <div class="ww-grid">
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">6:35 AM ET</div><div class="ww-lbl">Weekday 18:35 CST</div></div>
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">2:00 AM ET</div><div class="ww-lbl">Weekend 14:00 CST</div></div>
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">Most accessible</div><div class="ww-lbl">Of any Asian league</div></div>
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val neon-val">FREE</div><div class="ww-lbl">Wei Chuan on YT</div></div>
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">Jul 19–20</div><div class="ww-lbl">All-Star Weekend</div></div>
      <div class="ww-item"><div class="ww-val">Oct 18–26</div><div class="ww-lbl">Taiwan Series</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-num">01</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Where to Watch CPBL</h2>
      <span class="section-sub">Verified Apr 2026</span>
    </div>
    <div class="platforms">

      <div class="platform-card premium">
        <div class="platform-tag">Primary · All Games</div>
        <div class="platform-name">HamiVideo (CPBL TV)</div>
        <div class="platform-cost">~$10.30 / month</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          <strong>Full league service</strong> — every game, all six teams, full HD. Mandarin commentary. Taiwan's primary CPBL streaming home. Accepts international credit cards. This is the paid tier if you want everything.
        </div>
        <a href="https://hamivideo.hinet.net" target="_blank" class="platform-link">hamivideo.hinet.net →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="platform-card free">
        <div class="platform-tag tag-free">Free · Home Games</div>
        <div class="platform-name">Wei Chuan Dragons YouTube</div>
        <div class="platform-cost free">FREE</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          <strong>Every Wei Chuan home game, free, on YouTube.</strong> Deliberate strategy to build international fan base. Search 'Wei Chuan Dragons' on YouTube — the channel is a gift to international baseball fans. Free entry point to CPBL.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="platform-card free">
        <div class="platform-tag tag-free">Free · Select + Minors</div>
        <div class="platform-name">CPBL Official YouTube</div>
        <div class="platform-cost free">FREE</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          Highlights, select free live games, minor league and farm team broadcasts. Complements HamiVideo. Great for casual fans sampling the league.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="platform-card premium">
        <div class="platform-tag">Per-Team</div>
        <div class="platform-name">Team Twitch Channels</div>
        <div class="platform-cost">Varies by club</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          Each team operates its own Twitch stream for home games. Subscriptions and coverage vary by club. Rakuten Monkeys, Uni-Lions, and CTBC Brothers all maintain active Twitch presences.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="platform-card premium">
        <div class="platform-tag">Domestic</div>
        <div class="platform-name">Eleven Sports Network</div>
        <div class="platform-cost">Taiwan cable</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          Full Taiwanese TV coverage. Geoblocked outside Taiwan. If you live in Taipei, this is your cable option.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="platform-card premium">
        <div class="platform-tag">Select Markets</div>
        <div class="platform-name">iQiyi Sports</div>
        <div class="platform-cost">Subscription</div>
        <div class="platform-desc">
          Mainland China streaming service carrying select CPBL broadcasts. Limited international availability.
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-num">02</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">2026 Season Key Dates</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">Mar 28</div><div class="tl-title">Opening Day</div><div class="tl-desc">All 6 teams · 3 opening-weekend matchups. 6 games/week, no games on Mondays.</div></div>
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">May</div><div class="tl-title">Regular Season Peak</div><div class="tl-desc">Mid-season grind · Wei Chuan free streams prime viewing window.</div></div>
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">Jul 19–20</div><div class="tl-title">All-Star Weekend</div><div class="tl-desc">Home Run Derby + All-Star Game.</div></div>
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">Oct 10</div><div class="tl-title">Playoffs Begin</div><div class="tl-desc">Top 4 teams · best-of-5 semifinals.</div></div>
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">Oct 18–26</div><div class="tl-title">Taiwan Series</div><div class="tl-desc">Best-of-7 championship. Rakuten Monkeys are 2025 defending champs.</div></div>
      <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-date">Nov 15–Dec 7</div><div class="tl-title">Asia Winter League</div><div class="tl-desc">CPBL-hosted prospect showcase with NPB, KBO, and JABA teams.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-num">03</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">The 6 Teams</h2>
      <span class="section-sub">2026 · CPBL League</span>
    </div>
    <div class="divisions-wrap">
      <div class="div-block">
        <div class="div-title">CPBL · 6 Teams</div>
        <div class="div-teams">
          <div class="team-row"><strong>Rakuten Monkeys</strong> — Taoyuan · Taoyuan International Stadium · 2025 Taiwan Series Champions</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>CTBC Brothers</strong> — Taichung · Taichung Intercontinental Stadium · 2024 Champions</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>Uni-President 7-Eleven Lions</strong> — Tainan · Tainan Municipal Stadium · Most titles (10)</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>Fubon Guardians</strong> — New Taipei · Xinzhuang Stadium</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>Wei Chuan Dragons</strong> — Xinzhuang / Taoyuan · YouTube-native · Free home games 🆓</div>
          <div class="team-row"><strong>TSG Hawks</strong> — Taichung · Expansion team, joined 2024 · Ex-AWL champions 2023</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="did-you-know">
    <div class="dyk-badge">The Fact</div>
    <div class="dyk-title">Taiwan Won the 2024 Premier12 — And Nobody in America Noticed</div>
    <div class="dyk-body">
      In November 2024, Chinese Taipei — powered entirely by CPBL veterans and MLB prospects returning home — won the <strong>WBSC Premier12 championship</strong>, defeating Japan 4-0 in the final at Tokyo Dome. It was the biggest upset in international baseball since the 2006 WBC. The tournament confirmed what CPBL fans had been arguing for years: <strong>Taiwan's top flight produces legitimate big-league talent</strong>. The 2026 WBC roster for Chinese Taipei was built around CPBL players, and Taiwan reached pool play at Tokyo Dome with genuine MLB attention. When you tune in to a Rakuten Monkeys game at 6:35 AM ET, you're watching players who could be wearing an MLB uniform by 2027. The pipeline is real. And Wei Chuan is streaming it for free.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="watch-window neon">
    <div class="ww-title">⚡ CPBL This Week</div>
    <div class="ww-lede">See every CPBL game this week with matchups, times in NYC/ET, and streaming links — in the <strong>Official Viewer's Guide</strong>.</div>
